WEBVTT

00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:34.750 line:80%
[Qingfeng Stronghold]

00:01:30.839 --> 00:01:32.920 line:80%
Buddy, you're awake.

00:01:34.029 --> 00:01:34.640 line:80%
Come on.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.820 line:80%
[Second Master of Qingfeng Stronghold]

00:01:35.510 --> 00:01:36.640 line:80%
Have a drink with us.

00:01:43.309 --> 00:01:45.480 line:80%
None of you can take a hit.

00:01:46.330 --> 00:01:49.510 line:80%
[Lady Shisan
Chief Master of Qingfeng Stronghold]

00:01:47.750 --> 00:01:49.000 line:80%
Who else wants some?

00:01:50.080 --> 00:01:51.720 line:80%
-You go!
-You go! Why don't you go?

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:52.750 line:80%
I wouldn't dare.

00:01:51.750 --> 00:01:55.750 line:80%
[Qingfeng Stronghold]

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:54.870 line:80%
You guys can't possibly beat my sister.

00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:56.029 line:80%
Don't end up taking a tumble

00:01:56.029 --> 00:01:57.760 line:80%
and embarrassing yourselves.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:02.110 line:80%
Do you know why
I'm the boss of Qingfeng Stronghold?

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:06.570 line:80%
[Qingfeng Stronghold]

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.390 line:80%
A bunch of lousy men—

00:02:04.950 --> 00:02:06.840 line:80%
you only know how to bully women.

00:02:08.270 --> 00:02:09.360 line:80%
Does anyone else

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:12.180 line:80%
want to come up
and try their luck with me?

00:02:14.520 --> 00:02:16.560 line:80%
A bunch of useless bastards.

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:18.800 line:80%
I'm done wasting time on you.

00:02:20.830 --> 00:02:22.230 line:80%
How about I give it a try?

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:28.390 line:80%
You were still unconscious
when we rescued you.

00:02:28.390 --> 00:02:29.360 line:80%
Your hand is injured.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:30.600 line:80%
Don't push yourself.

00:02:30.670 --> 00:02:31.990 line:80%
Just go back and rest.

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:35.740 line:80%
Our Lady Shisan is not to be trifled with.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.760 line:80%
Don't risk your life

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.230 line:80%
just to show off.

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:48.080 line:80%
I never bully women.

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:50.570 line:80%
I'll give you a one-hand handicap.

00:02:54.920 --> 00:02:56.830 line:80%
Great! Wonderful!

00:02:56.830 --> 00:02:58.040 line:80%
Fight! Fight!

00:02:58.040 --> 00:02:59.480 line:80%
Great! Let's see it!

00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:00.340 line:80%
Come on, fight!

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.879 line:80%
Bravo! Nice attack!

00:03:31.900 --> 00:03:35.220 line:80%
Bravo! Bravo!

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:37.150 line:80%
Bravo! Bravo!

00:03:37.180 --> 00:03:37.879 line:80%
Awesome!

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:39.950 line:80%
Bravo! Bravo!

00:05:22.980 --> 00:05:28.100 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:05:28.180 --> 00:05:30.840 line:80%
[Episode 18]

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:36.190 line:80%
Help! Bandits! Someone help us!

00:06:00.870 --> 00:06:01.920 line:80%
Who are you?

00:06:03.750 --> 00:06:04.990 line:80%
Our master wants to see you.

00:06:04.990 --> 00:06:05.600 line:80%
Please.

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:19.400 line:80%
My benefactor,

00:06:19.550 --> 00:06:21.360 line:80%
I thank you for saving my life.

00:06:22.800 --> 00:06:23.600 line:80%
Come up.

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:25.720 line:80%
Mother!

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:26.520 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:29.160 line:80%
Let go of my mother!

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.440 line:80%
No need to repay me later.

00:06:33.670 --> 00:06:35.550 line:80%
Just submit yourself to me now.

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:38.400 line:80%
Mr. Qi?

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:40.150 line:80%
It's you.

00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:41.520 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:45.959 line:80%
In this world, apart from me,

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:49.430 line:80%
who else would care for you so deeply

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:52.280 line:80%
as to come and save you
before the city falls?

00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:11.410 line:80%
Here's your reward.

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:25.310 line:80%
S-So it was you.

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:33.230 line:80%
Why has your face changed?

00:07:33.690 --> 00:07:34.780 line:80%
Does this face

00:07:35.310 --> 00:07:36.310 line:80%
look good?

00:07:38.310 --> 00:07:39.840 line:80%
If I hadn't fixed this face,

00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:44.959 line:80%
how could I have brought myself
to see you?

00:08:04.230 --> 00:08:06.830 line:80%
You dare kill our men?
You're asking for death!

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:09.840 line:80%
How impudent!
Do you even know who's in this carriage?

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.110 line:80%
Stop!

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.230 line:80%
Get lost!

00:08:22.650 --> 00:08:23.310 line:80%
Min.

00:08:23.550 --> 00:08:24.280 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:27.110 line:80%
Weren't you headed to Lucheng?

00:08:27.110 --> 00:08:28.570 line:80%
How come you're in Lin'an?

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:30.990 line:80%
I heard you fell into the river
and went missing, Yuanqing,

00:08:30.990 --> 00:08:32.310 line:80%
and I was beside myself with worry,

00:08:32.310 --> 00:08:33.770 line:80%
so I came to find you first.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.000 line:80%
Are you injured?

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:40.370 line:80%
It's just a scratch. Nothing serious.

00:08:41.160 --> 00:08:43.430 line:80%
Min, go wait for me at Baxia first.

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.070 line:80%
Then we'll go to Lucheng together.

00:08:45.070 --> 00:08:46.470 line:80%
Even if Father flies into a rage,

00:08:46.470 --> 00:08:48.000 line:80%
I'll take the blame for you.

00:08:49.590 --> 00:08:51.920 line:80%
What about you? Aren't you coming with me?

00:08:53.430 --> 00:08:54.760 line:80%
I spent a fortune to bring

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:57.120 line:80%
all the bandits of Qingfeng Stronghold
under my command.

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.850 line:80%
This will be my big "gift"
to the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:01.920 line:80%
Since they all prioritize Lucheng,

00:09:02.670 --> 00:09:05.550 line:80%
I'll slaughter all the citizens
around here

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.640 line:80%
and strip him of all public support.

00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:10.000 line:80%
I set up that grain-buying scheme

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:11.280 line:80%
to help you,

00:09:11.670 --> 00:09:12.800 line:80%
but I never expected

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:15.190 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an
to turn my plan against me.

00:09:15.190 --> 00:09:17.250 line:80%
You must be extra careful from now on.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:20.240 line:80%
They say the Marquis of Wu'an
never miscalculates.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:22.770 line:80%
But maybe this time,
I've found his weak spot.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:26.470 line:80%
Yuanqing, you've learned from
the Marquis of Wu'an since childhood.

00:09:26.470 --> 00:09:27.670 line:80%
Knowing him as you do,

00:09:27.670 --> 00:09:29.040 line:80%
you've already outshone him.

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:31.640 line:80%
You were born to defeat him.

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.920 line:80%
Min, with your unparalleled strategy

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:36.280 line:80%
and my courage and strength,

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:38.550 line:80%
this world is destined to be ours.

00:09:39.080 --> 00:09:39.670 line:80%
You bet.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:50.430 line:80%
I said I'd help you
find this woman before, Min.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:53.350 line:80%
Looks like I was meddling.

00:10:01.710 --> 00:10:02.590 line:80%
Guys!

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:04.540 line:80%
Follow me into the county town

00:10:04.950 --> 00:10:06.590 line:80%
and get my woman back as well!

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:07.240 line:80%
Hyah!

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:20.560 line:80%
[Luo's Pawnshop]

00:10:31.710 --> 00:10:33.070 line:80%
Let's go! That way!

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:51.600 line:80%
[Lin'an]

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.070 line:80%
Help! Help!

00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:23.190 line:80%
Move!

00:12:23.710 --> 00:12:24.240 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:25.330 line:80%
-Faster!
-Move!

00:12:25.520 --> 00:12:26.070 line:80%
Kneel!

00:12:26.430 --> 00:12:26.950 line:80%
Kneel!

00:12:27.640 --> 00:12:28.240 line:80%
Kneel!

00:12:31.640 --> 00:12:34.160 line:80%
They say you guys know that butcher lady.

00:12:34.590 --> 00:12:36.880 line:80%
Tell me, what is her name,

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.590 line:80%
and where is she?

00:12:39.400 --> 00:12:40.400 line:80%
Whoever speaks

00:12:41.520 --> 00:12:42.670 line:80%
will live.

00:12:59.160 --> 00:13:00.120 line:80%
You speak.

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.040 line:80%
Sir,

00:13:03.640 --> 00:13:05.830 line:80%
I don't know who you're talking about.

00:13:11.310 --> 00:13:13.240 line:80%
This is what you get for fooling me.

00:13:13.430 --> 00:13:14.550 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:17.160 line:80%
You just hooked up with Lady Shisan,

00:13:17.470 --> 00:13:19.920 line:80%
and you're already looking for
another woman?

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:20.710 line:80%
Exactly.

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:22.310 line:80%
Our Chief Master is hot-tempered

00:13:22.310 --> 00:13:23.430 line:80%
and holds grudges.

00:13:23.430 --> 00:13:26.360 line:80%
You'd better be careful,
or you might lose your life.

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:31.280 line:80%
I'm not doing this out of desire—

00:13:33.190 --> 00:13:34.430 line:80%
it's for revenge.

00:13:52.090 --> 00:13:52.970 line:80%
You speak.

00:13:58.280 --> 00:14:00.070 line:80%
I... don't... know!

00:14:13.400 --> 00:14:15.650 line:80%
Run!

00:14:18.520 --> 00:14:19.670 line:80%
Run!

00:14:24.070 --> 00:14:25.550 line:80%
Loose the arrows! Shoot them dead!

00:14:25.550 --> 00:14:26.160 line:80%
Hurry!

00:14:29.950 --> 00:14:31.000 line:80%
Run!

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:35.840 line:80%
One got away! Bring her back!

00:15:17.800 --> 00:15:18.760 line:80%
You speak.

00:15:21.710 --> 00:15:23.160 line:80%
You bastard, I...

00:15:24.160 --> 00:15:26.290 line:80%
Don't know!

00:15:41.670 --> 00:15:42.830 line:80%
You'd better

00:15:44.190 --> 00:15:45.470 line:80%
truly not know.

00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:49.610 line:80%
You've killed my father

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:52.070 line:80%
and my mother.

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:55.990 line:80%
What's the point of me living alone?

00:15:58.240 --> 00:15:59.950 line:80%
You beast.

00:16:02.220 --> 00:16:03.750 line:80%
Kill me if you have the guts.

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:06.280 line:80%
Kill me!

00:16:11.590 --> 00:16:13.990 line:80%
You've got more backbone than your father.

00:16:15.640 --> 00:16:17.000 line:80%
I'll grant your wish!

00:16:33.640 --> 00:16:36.590 line:80%
I assume you don't know either.

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:39.470 line:80%
I... I know! I know!

00:16:39.710 --> 00:16:41.640 line:80%
I know! I know. I know!

00:16:41.710 --> 00:16:42.750 line:80%
I know.

00:16:42.800 --> 00:16:45.040 line:80%
My Lord, that butcher lady you mentioned,

00:16:45.040 --> 00:16:46.710 line:80%
her... Her name is Fan Changyu.

00:16:46.710 --> 00:16:47.590 line:80%
I... I know her!

00:16:47.590 --> 00:16:49.120 line:80%
She lives right over there.

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:50.640 line:80%
I can take you there right now.

00:16:50.640 --> 00:16:52.310 line:80%
Please spare my life, My Lord!

00:16:52.400 --> 00:16:54.350 line:80%
Shut up. Enough. Lead the way.

00:16:54.520 --> 00:16:55.310 line:80%
We won't kill you. Come on.

00:16:55.310 --> 00:16:55.950 line:80%
Okay.

00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:06.000 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:09.800 line:80%
My Lord, this is it.

00:17:14.280 --> 00:17:16.310 line:80%
My Lord, this is it.

00:17:16.550 --> 00:17:18.149 line:80%
This is Fan Changyu's house.

00:17:18.720 --> 00:17:20.280 line:80%
Are you sure this is the place?

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:21.520 line:80%
You didn't bring us to the wrong house,
did you?

00:17:21.520 --> 00:17:22.590 line:80%
I'm sure. I'm sure.

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:25.090 line:80%
Oh right, she raises pigs in her backyard.

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.680 line:80%
You don't believe me?

00:17:29.960 --> 00:17:31.620 line:80%
Come, I'll show you right now.

00:17:46.550 --> 00:17:49.350 line:80%
I despise disloyal people like this
the most—

00:17:49.680 --> 00:17:51.490 line:80%
betraying even their own.

00:17:53.070 --> 00:17:53.830 line:80%
Dying like this

00:17:53.830 --> 00:17:54.960 line:80%
is too easy for her.

00:17:56.070 --> 00:17:57.670 line:80%
Drag her body out and flog it.

00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:11.450 line:80%
How can you be so heartless, woman?

00:20:11.590 --> 00:20:12.590 line:80%
I came to find you,

00:20:12.800 --> 00:20:14.070 line:80%
yet you want my life.

00:20:14.520 --> 00:20:15.630 line:80%
I'll show you

00:20:15.960 --> 00:20:17.560 line:80%
what true heartlessness is!

00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:18.830 line:80%
If I die here,

00:20:19.590 --> 00:20:23.190 line:80%
you and the people in the cellar
won't stand a chance of escaping.

00:20:26.520 --> 00:20:27.480 line:80%
Let me go,

00:20:28.260 --> 00:20:30.860 line:80%
and I'll spare you
and the people in the cellar.

00:20:32.310 --> 00:20:33.570 line:80%
Why should I trust you?

00:20:34.110 --> 00:20:35.000 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:20:40.910 --> 00:20:42.800 line:80%
Then take a gamble and see.

00:20:45.310 --> 00:20:46.200 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:48.830 line:80%
Your Highness?

00:20:50.570 --> 00:20:52.370 line:80%
Your Highness, are you alright?

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:00.200 line:80%
Your Highness?

00:21:00.200 --> 00:21:01.060 line:80%
Your Highness?

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:05.480 line:80%
Hey, what's going on here?

00:21:07.390 --> 00:21:08.480 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:11.480 line:80%
so this is the "revenge"
you were talking about?

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.340 line:80%
Isn't this way of getting revenge

00:21:13.410 --> 00:21:14.760 line:80%
even more gratifying?

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:15.960 line:80%
Get lost.

00:21:16.720 --> 00:21:18.070 line:80%
I'm not done yet.

00:21:19.550 --> 00:21:20.440 line:80%
Alright, alright.

00:21:20.440 --> 00:21:22.070 line:80%
Please go on. Go on.

00:21:29.590 --> 00:21:31.390 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an saw this,

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.600 line:80%
wouldn't he be heartbroken?

00:21:34.910 --> 00:21:36.910 line:80%
What does this have to do with
the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:21:36.910 --> 00:21:37.680 line:80%
What?

00:21:38.440 --> 00:21:40.720 line:80%
Still dare not admit you're his woman?

00:21:44.170 --> 00:21:46.710 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an, Xie Zheng]

00:21:48.350 --> 00:21:49.150 line:80%
Right.

00:21:50.960 --> 00:21:52.350 line:80%
I admire the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:21:52.350 --> 00:21:53.750 line:80%
and I want to be his woman.

00:21:54.630 --> 00:21:56.490 line:80%
What does that have to do with you?

00:21:59.910 --> 00:22:01.520 line:80%
Why don't you try and see

00:22:02.870 --> 00:22:04.870 line:80%
between me and the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:22:05.490 --> 00:22:07.420 line:80%
who is better at caring for a woman?

00:22:12.550 --> 00:22:13.280 line:80%
Come.

00:22:25.070 --> 00:22:26.600 line:80%
You're holding me hostage,

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.960 line:80%
so I have to make it look real, right?

00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:31.240 line:80%
How else can I get you out?

00:22:32.230 --> 00:22:36.160 line:80%
How else can I help you hide the fact
that there're people in the cellar?

00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:40.000 line:80%
If your blade had gone 2 cun deeper,

00:22:40.390 --> 00:22:41.590 line:80%
I'd have been killed.

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:43.800 line:80%
What,

00:22:44.350 --> 00:22:46.870 line:80%
do you wish to take on 100 men
by yourself?

00:22:46.870 --> 00:22:47.870 line:80%
You talk too much.

00:22:49.840 --> 00:22:50.650 line:80%
Behave!

00:22:57.520 --> 00:22:58.780 line:80%
Second Master is here.

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:10.760 line:80%
What's this supposed to mean,
Second Master?

00:23:10.760 --> 00:23:14.440 line:80%
You want to take this woman
back to Qingfeng Stronghold?

00:23:16.630 --> 00:23:18.890 line:80%
I've finally found someone to my liking.

00:23:20.350 --> 00:23:22.150 line:80%
If you want to marry Lady Shisan,

00:23:22.680 --> 00:23:24.240 line:80%
kill this woman.

00:23:28.350 --> 00:23:29.520 line:80%
Second Master, so you expect me

00:23:29.520 --> 00:23:31.920 line:80%
to stay loyal to Lady Shisan
my entire life,

00:23:31.950 --> 00:23:33.390 line:80%
to be devoted to only her?

00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:37.200 line:80%
You've got 4 wives, Second Master,

00:23:37.310 --> 00:23:39.720 line:80%
and the number of women
you've taken is beyond count.

00:23:39.720 --> 00:23:40.960 line:80%
We are both men.

00:23:41.800 --> 00:23:44.350 line:80%
Why do you demand that of me?

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:47.710 line:80%
You're not wrong, actually.

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:49.880 line:80%
But with my sister's temper,

00:23:50.440 --> 00:23:52.310 line:80%
if she found out you brought another woman

00:23:52.310 --> 00:23:53.630 line:80%
back to Qingfeng Stronghold,

00:23:53.630 --> 00:23:55.200 line:80%
she'd kill you.

00:23:55.800 --> 00:23:57.600 line:80%
When I return to the stronghold,

00:23:57.720 --> 00:23:59.050 line:80%
I'll explain it myself.

00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:00.680 line:80%
Fine.

00:24:01.350 --> 00:24:02.000 line:80%
Let's go.

00:24:02.350 --> 00:24:03.680 line:80%
Back to the stronghold.

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:11.680 line:80%
Get on the horse, quick.

00:24:21.630 --> 00:24:22.830 line:80%
This trick again!

00:24:33.630 --> 00:24:34.830 line:80%
Someone! Help!

00:24:36.720 --> 00:24:39.390 line:80%
His Highness is taken hostage!
Quick, save His Highness!

00:24:39.390 --> 00:24:41.050 line:80%
You idiots!

00:24:44.910 --> 00:24:46.640 line:80%
I have to lure the bandits away.

00:24:46.650 --> 00:24:49.310 line:80%
Only then will Changning and the others
be safe.

00:24:55.280 --> 00:24:56.760 line:80%
You bastards! Come and catch me!

00:24:56.760 --> 00:24:57.820 line:80%
-Catch her!
-Hyah!

00:24:58.480 --> 00:25:00.350 line:80%
Your Highness! Wake up! Your Highness!

00:25:00.350 --> 00:25:01.680 line:80%
Stop! Stop right there!

00:25:03.110 --> 00:25:03.910 line:80%
Stop!

00:25:04.240 --> 00:25:05.040 line:80%
Don't run!

00:25:05.310 --> 00:25:05.910 line:80%
Catch her!

00:25:07.110 --> 00:25:08.390 line:80%
His Highness's woman is trying to escape!

00:25:08.390 --> 00:25:10.390 line:80%
Bring some men and help me chase her!

00:25:10.480 --> 00:25:12.110 line:80%
-Stop!
-After her!

00:25:14.910 --> 00:25:16.240 line:80%
Grandma, I'm hungry...

00:25:17.110 --> 00:25:19.000 line:80%
Quiet. Just wait a little longer.

00:25:19.310 --> 00:25:20.280 line:80%
In a while,

00:25:20.280 --> 00:25:22.280 line:80%
I'll heat up some dumplings for you.

00:25:36.870 --> 00:25:38.070 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:39.190 --> 00:25:40.350 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:43.910 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:45.070 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:46.280 --> 00:25:47.310 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:49.240 --> 00:25:50.280 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:51.830 --> 00:25:54.150 line:80%
Sister.

00:25:55.720 --> 00:25:58.390 line:80%
Sister, where are you?

00:25:59.070 --> 00:26:00.550 line:80%
Sister.

00:26:03.240 --> 00:26:06.280 line:80%
Sister, where are you?

00:26:09.310 --> 00:26:12.320 line:80%
Sister, where are you?

00:26:12.960 --> 00:26:13.760 line:80%
Over there.

00:26:14.040 --> 00:26:15.170 line:80%
Go check over there.

00:26:16.280 --> 00:26:17.080 line:80%
There. There!

00:26:20.590 --> 00:26:22.280 line:80%
Why don't I see Changning?

00:26:22.590 --> 00:26:23.850 line:80%
Changning has asthma.

00:26:23.910 --> 00:26:26.240 line:80%
She can't stay in this cellar
for too long.

00:26:26.350 --> 00:26:28.590 line:80%
Changyu has hidden her in a safe place.

00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:30.770 line:80%
I'll go check upstairs.

00:26:50.830 --> 00:26:51.630 line:80%
Changning?

00:26:52.870 --> 00:26:53.720 line:80%
Changning?

00:26:55.150 --> 00:26:56.000 line:80%
Changning?

00:26:58.650 --> 00:27:00.800 line:80%
[Lin'an]

00:28:23.350 --> 00:28:24.590 line:80%
Why aren't you running anymore?

00:28:24.590 --> 00:28:25.720 line:80%
Why did you stop?

00:28:28.350 --> 00:28:29.110 line:80%
Attack!

00:28:50.550 --> 00:28:51.550 line:80%
Loose the arrows!

00:29:21.910 --> 00:29:22.800 line:80%
Second Master!

00:29:23.070 --> 00:29:24.150 line:80%
Second Master!

00:29:24.280 --> 00:29:25.350 line:80%
This is outrageous!

00:29:25.350 --> 00:29:26.810 line:80%
Avenge the Second Master!

00:29:26.870 --> 00:29:27.830 line:80%
After her!

00:29:49.830 --> 00:29:51.740 line:80%
News came that
you were in danger on the battlefield.

00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:53.310 line:80%
Though the Prime Minister
didn't speak of it,

00:29:53.310 --> 00:29:54.480 line:80%
he was deeply worried,

00:29:54.480 --> 00:29:56.000 line:80%
unable to sleep day or night.

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:58.520 line:80%
Now that he's learned
you've recovered and escaped danger,

00:29:58.520 --> 00:30:00.380 line:80%
he specially sent me to visit you.

00:30:00.800 --> 00:30:02.310 line:80%
I didn't expect to run into you
along the way.

00:30:02.310 --> 00:30:04.040 line:80%
I appreciate Uncle's concern.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:06.570 line:80%
Senior, please also convey this to Uncle:

00:30:07.280 --> 00:30:08.310 line:80%
I'm hard to kill

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:09.810 line:80%
and managed to survive.

00:30:10.630 --> 00:30:13.440 line:80%
I bet the one who tried to kill me

00:30:14.200 --> 00:30:16.130 line:80%
must be losing sleep over it by now.

00:30:18.440 --> 00:30:19.910 line:80%
We've been fellow apprentices for years,

00:30:19.910 --> 00:30:21.640 line:80%
and I should've protected you.

00:30:21.830 --> 00:30:23.090 line:80%
But unfortunately...

00:30:23.780 --> 00:30:25.650 line:80%
I had no choice, you know.

00:30:27.150 --> 00:30:27.960 line:80%
It's fine.

00:30:28.390 --> 00:30:31.850 line:80%
Even though you were physically
by the Prime Minister's side,

00:30:32.150 --> 00:30:34.830 line:80%
it's enough that your heart was with me.

00:30:38.280 --> 00:30:41.240 line:80%
What are your plans for Lucheng now?

00:30:41.870 --> 00:30:43.110 line:80%
Plans?

00:30:43.550 --> 00:30:45.280 line:80%
I'm not even fully recovered from
my injuries yet.

00:30:45.280 --> 00:30:48.140 line:80%
General He Jingyuan is holding the fort
in Lucheng.

00:30:48.200 --> 00:30:51.070 line:80%
Wei Xuan was supposed to stay here
supervising the troops,

00:30:51.070 --> 00:30:52.800 line:80%
which would've let me slack off a bit,

00:30:52.800 --> 00:30:55.460 line:80%
but that brat suddenly
went back to the capital.

00:30:55.680 --> 00:30:56.680 line:80%
For now,

00:30:56.680 --> 00:30:58.240 line:80%
I can only keep my soldiers

00:30:58.240 --> 00:30:59.310 line:80%
safe and sound.

00:30:59.910 --> 00:31:04.240 line:80%
Only then will I have the strength
to take revenge and restore my honor, right?

00:31:08.590 --> 00:31:09.450 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:31:09.680 --> 00:31:11.740 line:80%
The falcon has returned from Lin'an.

00:31:16.550 --> 00:31:17.280 line:80%
Lin'an?

00:31:19.910 --> 00:31:21.590 line:80%
Muster 100 Blood-Robed Cavalry soldiers
and follow me to Lin'an!

00:31:21.590 --> 00:31:22.720 line:80%
Yes, Your Lordship.

00:31:26.680 --> 00:31:27.680 line:80%
Search the place!

00:31:43.150 --> 00:31:45.550 line:80%
Xiaohu, does your tooth still hurt?

00:31:45.550 --> 00:31:47.310 line:80%
It stopped hurting a while ago.

00:31:53.310 --> 00:31:55.310 line:80%
Has this room been searched?

00:31:55.630 --> 00:31:56.800 line:80%
It's a complete mess inside,

00:31:56.800 --> 00:31:58.660 line:80%
so we've definitely searched it.

00:31:58.800 --> 00:32:00.960 line:80%
Wait. We haven't searched in here.

00:32:01.070 --> 00:32:02.760 line:80%
Go in and search!

00:32:04.310 --> 00:32:05.110 line:80%
Xiaohu.

00:32:05.910 --> 00:32:08.110 line:80%
The dumplings are covered on the stove.

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:09.590 line:80%
Heat up 5 at a time.

00:32:10.310 --> 00:32:11.370 line:80%
Don't eat too much.

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:13.630 line:80%
Six is okay too.

00:32:13.830 --> 00:32:16.230 line:80%
If you eat too much,
your stomach will hurt.

00:32:18.070 --> 00:32:19.800 line:80%
The cured meat in the yard

00:32:19.830 --> 00:32:21.550 line:80%
will last until the snow melts.

00:32:21.550 --> 00:32:23.390 line:80%
Feed the chickens with millet.

00:32:24.390 --> 00:32:25.440 line:80%
When the chickens lay eggs,

00:32:25.440 --> 00:32:26.830 line:80%
don't eat them all.

00:32:29.070 --> 00:32:30.470 line:80%
As long as there are eggs,

00:32:30.960 --> 00:32:32.270 line:80%
you can hatch chicks.

00:32:34.760 --> 00:32:37.290 line:80%
Then you'll have eggs to eat
and won't starve.

00:32:38.240 --> 00:32:40.170 line:80%
Wait for your brother to come back.

00:32:49.720 --> 00:32:52.150 line:80%
You must not go out before dawn.

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:52.520 line:80%
Who?

00:33:52.910 --> 00:33:53.800 line:80%
Who is it?

00:34:04.350 --> 00:34:05.830 line:80%
You bastards!

00:34:06.150 --> 00:34:07.720 line:80%
I'll fight you to the death!

00:34:14.080 --> 00:34:15.560 line:80%
I'm just an old woman

00:34:15.950 --> 00:34:17.280 line:80%
with no children!

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:19.200 line:80%
I'm not afraid of you!

00:34:19.310 --> 00:34:21.120 line:80%
You motherless scum!

00:34:21.120 --> 00:34:22.680 line:80%
You motherless scum!

00:34:23.430 --> 00:34:24.830 line:80%
You beasts!

00:34:36.430 --> 00:34:37.800 line:80%
Darn old hag.

00:34:37.990 --> 00:34:39.240 line:80%
Rambling on and on

00:34:39.510 --> 00:34:40.720 line:80%
with your filthy mouth—

00:34:40.720 --> 00:34:42.830 line:80%
you deserve to die alone.

00:35:31.510 --> 00:35:34.350 line:80%
Young lady. Nowhere for you
to run now, huh?

00:35:34.760 --> 00:35:36.290 line:80%
Just submit yourself to me.

00:35:39.800 --> 00:35:42.130 line:80%
I'm much better than the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:44.720 line:80%
If you submit to me, I'll spare your life.

00:35:52.820 --> 00:35:54.480 line:80%
If you take another step back,

00:35:54.800 --> 00:35:56.730 line:80%
you'll die without a burial place.

00:36:19.640 --> 00:36:20.560 line:80%
Report!

00:36:20.760 --> 00:36:21.350 line:80%
Report!

00:36:21.720 --> 00:36:22.350 line:80%
Report...

00:36:23.120 --> 00:36:25.980 line:80%
Your Highness, our stronghold
has been massacred.

00:36:26.350 --> 00:36:27.280 line:80%
Who did it?

00:36:27.390 --> 00:36:29.470 line:80%
The survivors from the stronghold say

00:36:29.470 --> 00:36:31.390 line:80%
it was the Marquis of Wu'an's
Blood-Robed Cavalry.

00:36:31.390 --> 00:36:33.120 line:80%
There were at least 100 men.

00:36:34.950 --> 00:36:36.430 line:80%
No wonder.

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:38.680 line:80%
With 100 Blood-Robed Cavalry soldiers,

00:36:38.680 --> 00:36:41.080 line:80%
taking a whole city would be
a piece of cake,

00:36:41.640 --> 00:36:43.900 line:80%
let alone the tiny Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:37:01.800 --> 00:37:02.660 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:37:02.830 --> 00:37:03.720 line:80%
We've searched the entire stronghold,

00:37:03.720 --> 00:37:04.800 line:80%
but we didn't find Mrs. Fan

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:06.330 line:80%
or anyone from Lin'an Town.

00:37:06.720 --> 00:37:07.800 line:80%
Lin'an Town was massacred too.

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:08.720 line:80%
We saved some survivors,

00:37:08.720 --> 00:37:10.430 line:80%
but Mrs. Fan wasn't among them.

00:37:10.430 --> 00:37:11.830 line:80%
We've also searched all of Xigu Lane,

00:37:11.830 --> 00:37:14.360 line:80%
but there was no sign of
Mrs. Fan or Changning.

00:37:44.310 --> 00:37:45.160 line:80%
Go find her.

00:37:49.640 --> 00:37:50.430 line:80%
Let's go!

00:39:05.620 --> 00:39:07.310 line:80%
♪ I just don't want to ♪

00:39:08.010 --> 00:39:08.860 line:80%
♪ Keep weighing every word ♪

00:39:08.880 --> 00:39:10.970 line:80%
♪ And hiding in time in silence ♪

00:39:12.060 --> 00:39:13.800 line:80%
♪ It's not that I don't believe in karma ♪

00:39:14.540 --> 00:39:16.620 line:80%
♪ That I'm being stubborn ♪

00:39:18.520 --> 00:39:19.980 line:80%
♪ Some endings have long been ♪

00:39:20.970 --> 00:39:22.180 line:80%
♪ Weathered through a thousand years ♪

00:39:21.800 --> 00:39:23.510 line:80%
Your Lordship, let me help you.

00:39:22.200 --> 00:39:23.770 line:80%
♪ Traced by those who come after ♪

00:39:24.760 --> 00:39:26.710 line:80%
♪ Compared to fading away in sorrow ♪

00:39:27.070 --> 00:39:29.200 line:80%
♪ I'd rather fight ♪

00:39:29.730 --> 00:39:32.660 line:80%
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

00:39:33.050 --> 00:39:35.530 line:80%
♪ Comes from love ♪

00:39:36.240 --> 00:39:38.860 line:80%
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:42.150 line:80%
♪ Like holing a torch in the wilderness ♪

00:39:42.780 --> 00:39:44.810 line:80%
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

00:39:45.350 --> 00:39:46.240 line:80%
Blood-Robed Cavalry!

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:48.510 line:80%
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

00:39:46.310 --> 00:39:46.950 line:80%
Yes!

00:39:47.280 --> 00:39:48.800 line:80%
Find somewhere to take shelter
from the snow and keep warm!

00:39:48.780 --> 00:39:51.800 line:80%
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

00:39:49.350 --> 00:39:49.950 line:80%
Yes!

00:39:52.430 --> 00:39:57.660 line:80%
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

00:39:59.430 --> 00:40:01.230 line:80%
Your Lordship, let us carry her.

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:02.720 line:80%
It's not your place.

00:40:02.720 --> 00:40:04.830 line:80%
Hang the bodies of
the Qingfeng Stronghold bandits

00:40:04.830 --> 00:40:05.870 line:80%
on the city walls, gut them open,

00:40:05.870 --> 00:40:07.730 line:80%
and leave them exposed for 3 days!

00:40:07.950 --> 00:40:08.680 line:80%
Yes.

00:40:26.650 --> 00:40:29.420 line:80%
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

00:40:29.850 --> 00:40:32.060 line:80%
♪ Comes from love ♪

00:40:33.160 --> 00:40:35.780 line:80%
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

00:40:36.150 --> 00:40:38.960 line:80%
♪ Like holing a torch in the wilderness ♪

00:40:39.590 --> 00:40:41.730 line:80%
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

00:40:42.600 --> 00:40:45.320 line:80%
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

00:40:45.670 --> 00:40:48.720 line:80%
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

00:40:49.180 --> 00:40:54.410 line:80%
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:51.560 line:80%
Changyu.

00:40:52.390 --> 00:40:53.240 line:80%
Changyu!

00:40:56.200 --> 00:40:56.870 line:80%
♪ Don't mind me ♪

00:40:56.900 --> 00:40:57.960 line:80%
♪ Everything has happened ♪

00:40:58.240 --> 00:41:01.580 line:80%
♪ A thousand years from now
no one's blood will remain warm ♪

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:04.380 line:80%
♪ Let them laugh and mock ♪

00:41:04.830 --> 00:41:07.920 line:80%
♪ As long as you remember me ♪

00:41:06.910 --> 00:41:07.760 line:80%
Changyu.

00:41:08.720 --> 00:41:09.290 line:80%
♪ Forget about ♪

00:41:09.310 --> 00:41:10.540 line:80%
♪ Leaving a name in history ♪

00:41:11.120 --> 00:41:14.230 line:80%
♪ I only want to leave a mark
in your life ♪

00:41:15.030 --> 00:41:16.480 line:80%
♪ I will let go ♪

00:41:16.680 --> 00:41:19.080 line:80%
Why aren't you the Fan Changyu I know?

00:41:17.460 --> 00:41:20.790 line:80%
♪ After taking this one last gamble ♪

00:41:19.950 --> 00:41:21.830 line:80%
The one who was always so warm...

00:41:21.400 --> 00:41:21.970 line:80%
♪ Forget about ♪

00:41:21.990 --> 00:41:23.180 line:80%
♪ The carved stones or constellations ♪

00:41:23.080 --> 00:41:25.200 line:80%
Why is your body so cold now?

00:41:23.740 --> 00:41:26.730 line:80%
♪ I'll cast all karma behind me ♪

00:41:27.610 --> 00:41:29.640 line:80%
♪ Beacon fires stir the lords ♪

00:41:30.010 --> 00:41:33.980 line:80%
♪ Unstoppable, ruthless fate ♪

00:41:37.200 --> 00:41:38.030 line:80%
Changyu.

00:41:38.720 --> 00:41:39.430 line:80%
Changyu.

00:41:40.280 --> 00:41:42.210 line:80%
I won't let anything happen to you.

00:41:42.870 --> 00:41:43.680 line:80%
Changyu.

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:46.510 line:80%
Changyu...

00:42:07.870 --> 00:42:10.800 line:80%
Severe cold has invaded her body,

00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:13.950 line:80%
and her pulse is weak.

00:42:15.200 --> 00:42:18.160 line:80%
She's at a critical juncture now.

00:42:19.160 --> 00:42:22.510 line:80%
She needs a scraping treatment
to stimulate her blood flow,

00:42:22.830 --> 00:42:25.080 line:80%
clear her meridians,

00:42:26.120 --> 00:42:30.310 line:80%
and dispel the cold from her body.

00:42:28.300 --> 00:42:30.100 line:80%
[Cinnabar]

00:42:37.640 --> 00:42:38.560 line:80%
Madam.

00:42:39.680 --> 00:42:40.740 line:80%
You know medicine?

00:42:41.510 --> 00:42:42.870 line:80%
A little.

00:42:43.200 --> 00:42:44.430 line:80%
Please save her life.

00:42:45.470 --> 00:42:47.120 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:42:47.350 --> 00:42:49.160 line:80%
my son and daughter-in-law

00:42:49.200 --> 00:42:51.200 line:80%
went to the city to sell medicine,

00:42:52.080 --> 00:42:54.720 line:80%
and I'm a blind old woman.

00:42:56.470 --> 00:42:59.560 line:80%
Is there any lady among you

00:42:59.870 --> 00:43:01.670 line:80%
who can help with the treatment?

00:43:05.120 --> 00:43:06.240 line:80%
I'm her husband.

00:43:06.990 --> 00:43:07.600 line:80%
I can do it.